## 📁 Projects

### 01 — HR Analytics Dashboard
**Tools:** Power BI, DAX, Power Query
**Dataset:** IBM HR Attrition (1,470 employees)
**Pages:** 6 pages | 25+ insights | 10 DAX measures

**Key Insights:**
- 16.12% overall attrition rate
- R&D has highest attrition (133 employees)
- Overtime employees show higher attrition risk
- Managers earn 5x more than Lab Technicians
- Peak attrition at Year 1 — onboarding risk identified

**DAX Measures:**
Total Employees | Total Attrition | Attrition Rate % |
Active Employees | Avg Monthly Income | Avg Tenure |
Avg Job Satisfaction | Dept Attrition %


